title: #92Noon!  10am Hour 8/17 - Vikes Bites, Greg Papa
description: Nordo highlights some matchups to look out for at Vikings/49ers joint practice.  49ers radio play-by-play announcer Greg Papa joins 92Noon to discuss Trey Lance, him & PA's 30+ year friendship, Vin Scully's death & more!
